arts.ttl: Argentina Predicted Lineup vs. Chile: World Cup Qualifying
arts.sum: Victory in Chile would further cement their place at the summit and given their upcoming opponents are currently languishing in bottom spot having lost over half of their qualifying matches, another triumph looks likely. La Albiceleste secured their place at the 2026 FIFA World Cup during the March international break and look destined to finish top of CONMEBOL qualifying.
